              We will definitely be sending him again when he's next due a
              haircut. We'll definitely recommend to all my friends & family
              who've got dogs. Thank you Shelley üòÄ
            </GoogleReview>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-slide">
            <GoogleReview
              author="Danielle Blackmore"
              avatar="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILaOn4TlM7mxe9BLYM38HC9t5100QnuelgpEf8USrKkoIdrQ=s40-c-rp-mo-br100"
            >
              Rocco's first groom at Popletts & he smells & feels divine! Never
              managed to get his claws so short so really happy with that! Your
              lovely Shelly thank you Rocco will definitely be back ‚ù§Ô∏è
            </GoogleReview>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-slide">
            <GoogleReview
              author="Gabrielle Reinbergs"
              avatar="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvHn3wnRGcI0f1mZULlPlPQFK8rFziLBk2E6sirelql-UFKA=s40-c-rp-mo-br100"
            >
              The best, our 18 month golden retriever is absolutely scared of
              everything and he was put at ease and well looked after. He came
              out super happy and excited, not to mention looking neat and
              handsome after his trim and smelling amazing. Thank you again! X
            </GoogleReview>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-slide">
            <GoogleReview
              author="Daniela Smith1998"
              avatar="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGQ_IB142mjRhU6M47gTnNTnj8u5k7riLKjd_z3E-bN4IRdQ=s40-c-rp-mo-br100"
            >
              5 star service from popletts today! What a wonderful friendly
              service! My dog didn't want to leave! His transformation is
              incredible truly an amazing service! Customer for life now. Thank
              you.
            </GoogleReview>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-slide">
            <GoogleReview
              author="Richard Worby"
              avatar="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL1MFwmBXhdb6--MPwEBV1NTUjBIBzjMCZVpoVh5Yr4SM3Dfg=s40-c-rp-mo-br100"
            >
              Took both my dogs otto and blessing shelly done a great job with
              both especially blessing who can be a bit snappy will definitely
              be going again x
            </GoogleReview>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-slide">
            <GoogleReview
              author="Laura Brickley"
              avatar="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-9nZTfEAvRAU0ntQpFS2yDXQyRziEDXvnLEXKYa2ZEFGr3Q=s40-c-rp-mo-br100"
            >
              Brilliant service will definitely use again
            </GoogleReview>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-slide">
            <GoogleReview
              author="Stacey Read"
              avatar="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKXncLyobXnirI8jun6XgHCL7iwrUQ8x7ybHMYxeYsuxwYJ0q3wQ=s40-c-rp-mo-br100"
            >
              Both our dogs looked and smelled awesome and loved getting a
              pamper and groom by Shelley. She is so lovely, calm and patient
              with the dogs. Highly recommend:)
            </GoogleReview>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-slide">
            <GoogleReview
              author="Daniela Pinzon Guzman"
              avatar="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXH0Grac_eoFNg_xcquS_-Vi8uyTEIXso-T53q_-D7nnQC8X2GdTg=s40-c-rp-mo-br100"
            >
              Shelley is the best option if you need your dog to look and smell
              fantastic. She is very professional and treats your dog with
              plenty of love. I highly recommend her and will definitely be
              coming back!
            </GoogleReview>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-slide">
            <GoogleReview
              author="James Firth"
              avatar="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXZJirr2_TikVCw8CZ9hnhFysWbzDSgGr4JaAVIbBKGPqqQg=s40-c-rp-mo-br100"
            >
              Thank you for grooming Casper so lovely. We absolutely love his
              new tail üòÄüêï. He looks so handsome and came back home happy and
